### 0c. Variable codebook (reference)

- **FIPS**: unique identifier for each county  
- **AveBMI**: county average BMI (BRFSS; kg/m²)  
- **AvePM**: annual average PM2.5 (AQS; μg/m³)  
- **NumTot**: total population  
- **PerBlack, PerLatinx, PerAsam, PerWhite**: racial composition  
- **MedHInc**: median household income  
- **MedHVal**: median household value (homeowners)  
- **FemaleUnemp, MaleUnemp**: unemployment rate by sex  
- **LTHS**: % adults with less than high school education  
- **ClimateRegion**: NOAA climate region category  

