## 7. Assess model assumptions

> **Class question — answer: four assumptions of a linear model**  
> 1. **Linearity** (mean of outcome is a linear function of predictors)  
> 2. **Independence** (errors are independent)  
> 3. **Homoscedasticity** (constant error variance)  
> 4. **Normality of errors** (errors approximately normal, mainly for inference)

